{"tid":2077314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[真送錢] UCLA 10分鐘問卷送你$200","createTime":"2020-06-24T07:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T14:37:54.000Z","uid":137255,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"643b5569cf446c122f220fcc840ede84a08f44bd","tid":2077314,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:47:43.000Z","msg":"如果你是一位出生於1996/01/01&nbsp;至1998/12/31期間的香港永久居民，你將合資格參與一個由美國加洲大學舉辦的社會問卷調查(約10分鐘長)。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n完成問卷後，你將會有1/ 15的機會獲得一張價值 ~<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HK$195 (US$25)&nbsp;的VISA現金禮卡</span></strong>。共110張電子禮卡將在兩星期被轉發至從1500名受訪者抽出的得獎者之電郵地址。<br />\n<a href=\"https://polisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp?source=goop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp%3Fsource%3Dgoop&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d266b356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://polisciucla.ca1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_eIMhAh2xxkRckqp?source=goop</a><br />\n<br />\nUCLA Department of Political Science"},{"pid":"cca639d5cbd55e84d92fbdc7e6da1b300ab92ba9","tid":2077314,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba050e8512bbf9e72e9ff2b34aee157492327d21","tid":2077314,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"留名睇research結果"}]}